Pauline Curley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pauline_Curley 0 Pauline Curley (December 19, 1903 – December 11, 2000) was a vaudeville and silent film actress from Holyoke, Massachusetts. Her film career spanned much of the silent era, from 1912-1929. Pauline_Curley ( December_19_,_1903 – December_11_,_2000 ) was a_vaudeville and silent_film_actress from Holyoke , Massachusetts .
